---
title: Crispy Spiced Chicken with Sweet Potato Fries and Garden Salad
description: Chicken gets a spicy crunch thanks to toasted panko and chili powder. Roasted sweet potato fries bring a hearty, sweet contrast, while a fresh garden salad brightens everything up.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5703c46afd2cb981468b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/5703c46afd2cb981468b4567.pdf
